      ${cmd2}${data2}${index2}${using2}with ${style2}${lines2}${points2}${color2}${title2}${axes2},\\\n\z
      ${cmd3}${data3}${index3}${using3}with ${style3}${lines3}${points3}${color3}${title3}${axes3},\\\n\z
