__help.gplot = [=[
NAME
  gplot

SYNOPSIS
  my_gplot = gplot 'mygplot' {}

DESCRIPTION
  gplot is used to manages gnuplot instances by creating it, and writing to it.
  Its unique state is the stream id (sid) of the instance it currently handles.

